{"tid":2438552,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政中心收到可疑粉末信件　60人一度疏散","createTime":"2021-03-08T14:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T16:02:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e547395cd5053bdd8b4a3b8c7697ba84d2a1f757","tid":2438552,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"中環律政中心收到一封粉末信件，警方調查後相信沒有危險成份，案件列作刑事恐嚇，暫時無人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n警方到律政中心調查。下午四時許，職員收到一封可疑信件，內藏白色粉末，於是報警。警方到場調查，60人一度疏散，經爆炸品處理課人員檢查後，相信該粉末無危險成份，檢走作進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n案件列作刑事恐嚇，暫時無人被捕，交由中區警區重案組調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426649&d=5FApYPwYYRZ83iNn2U1Rv2Z69rz5%2BYz%2FKt%2FQ7ZoV0Dw%3D&h=ccd6a5c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D426649&h=e0c40392\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=426649</a>"},{"pid":"6cf8c90f28fa5403a81237dada74cbd80b1acbb8","tid":2438552,"uid":306614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:47:08.000Z","msg":"麪粉都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037315e54aeaed5725d6bab15d5f97dddd52c4aa","tid":2438552,"uid":272677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無做衰野使撚驚，不過有做就... ..."},{"pid":"35f803634e737d80486cde9ff58a3f26bae3d10f","tid":2438552,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T14:56:42.000Z","msg":"Oncc話入面有啲退休法官嘅名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ce4e4a9529039272566562f8465547147490de","tid":2438552,"uid":68896,"like":3,"dislike":0,"